definitions.definition: Any one of several species of food fishes that make up the genus Alosa in the family Clupeidae , to which the herrings also belong; river herring .
Any bluefish of species Pomatomus saltatrix .

main_definition: Any one of several species of food fishes that make up the genus Alosa in the family Clupeidae , to which the herrings also belong; river herring .
secondary_definitions: ( South Africa ) Any bluefish of species Pomatomus saltatrix .
